snippet.title: SOLAR ASH | Introduction Trailer
snippet.description:
SOLAR ASH is coming to PS5, PS4, and the Epic Games Store in 2021. Wishlist on the Epic Games Store: https://www.epicgames.com/store/en-US/product/solar-ash-kingdom/home

Journey through a surreal, vivid and highly stylized world filled with mystery, wild high-speed traversal, endearing characters, and massive enemy encounters. The Void beckons…

Developed by HEART MACHINE. Published by Annapurna Interactive. 

© Annapurna Interactive, 2020
